"(Accidental poisoning by and exposure to other and unspecified drugs, medicaments and biological substances); X45 (Accidental"
"poisoning by and exposure to alcohol); X60 (Intentional self-poisoning by and exposure to nonopioid analgesics, antipyretics and"
"antirheumatics); X61 (Intentional self-poisoning by and exposure to antiepileptic, sedative-hypnotic, antiparkinsonism and"
"psychotropic drugs, not elsewhere classified); X62 (Intentional self-poisoning by and exposure to narcotics and psychodysleptics"
